  "keyFeatures": [
    "20+ state-of-the-art anomaly detection models (PatchCore, PaDiM, EfficientAD, WinCLIP, etc.)",
    "Dual Python API and CLI interface for training, inference, and benchmarking",
    "PyTorch Lightning-based implementations with minimal boilerplate",
    "OpenVINO export for accelerated inference on Intel hardware",
    "Support for image, video, and depth modalities",
    "One-class, zero-shot, and few-shot learning paradigms",
    "Hyperparameter optimization with Weights & Biases and Comet.ml",
    "Built-in benchmark datasets (MVTecAD, MVTecAD2, VisA, BTech, etc.)",
    "Anomalib Studio: low/no-code web UI for training and deployment",
    "Tiled ensemble pipeline for large-image processing"
  ],
